T1  - A Network Decomposition Approach for Approximating the Steady-State Behavior of Markovian Multi-Echelon Reparable Item Inventory Systems
AU  - Gross, Donald
AU  - Kioussis, Leonidas C.
AU  - Miller, Douglas R.
Y1  - 1987/11/01
PY  - 1987
DA  - 1987/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.33.11.1453
